As you guys have been asking… here’s what I’ve been using for my lips lately!!

From pigmented and dry to soft and naturally pink.. @mywishcare lip balm has been such a game-changer!😍

It’s not your regular balm..it’s got SPF 50 ++++ & kojic acid (like, how cool is that?!)
That combo helped lighten my lip pigmentation so much 
plus it keeps my lips hydrated without needing to reapply 100 times a day😮‍💨

The natural tint is super cute for no-makeup days too ✨
So yeah, if you’re dealing with dry lips, dark lips or just want something that actually works.
THIS IS IT!
